# NOAA CUDEM 1/9 arc-sec, all US coastal regions. Run from pipelines/:  just ../sources/cudem/
# Mirrored model: register every tile in NOAA's urllist as a relative objects/<key> row
# (header reads only for newly-listed tiles — the ~188 GB of bytes are copied into the
# store's object mirror separately, and aggregation range-reads them from there). Tiles
# are already COGs (NAVD88 / NAD83), so no normalize/datum/tarball.
[no-cd]
default:
    uv run python source_mirror.py cudem
